## libtmux 0.18.0 (2022-12-27)

### Breaking

- Server: Add `__repr__` and set `socket_path` if none set.

  Before (0.17 and below):

  ```python
  <libtmux.server.Server object at ...>
  ```

  New `__repr__` (0.18+):

  ```python
  Server(socket_name=test)
  ```

  ```python
  Server(socket_path=/tmp/tmux-1000/default)
  ```

